{
  "texts": [
    "Exclusion criteria.",
    "Non-peer-reviewed and non-English publications or resources were excluded.",
    "Studies were excluded if they (i) did not incorporate AI into their rehabilitation platform, (ii) did not evaluate their platform on patients, or (iii) did not evaluate their platform in patients' homes.",
    "If one or more of the above criteria were met, studies were excluded.",
    "It is to be noted that some AI and VRehab solutions may be delivered in a hospital or clinic setting."
  ]
}